divs: Sighting DetailsWhite egg shape orb traveling toward the bay very left side of U.S.101 as my car was traveling south this object caught my eye. The orb color was a weird off white gray.
Summary: Driving south on U.S.101 left of freeway saw white egg shape orb traveling to coast
